**OPERO Hotel Johor Bahru** is looking for suitable candidates for many positions available this 2020.

### About Opero Hotel 
At Opero. people are our priority. The hotel is designed uniquely for business and leisure in Southkey, Johor Bahru to create and deliver superior service, luxury and style. We take pride in our forward-thinking dynamic culture and are looking for individuals who want to be part of our community.
{% include link-adsense.html %} 
### Write in Positions
- Food and Beverage Manager
- Head Chef
- Front Office Manager
- Executive Housekeeper
- Maintenance Manager
- Assistant Security & Safety Manager
- Senior Sales Manager
- Human Resources Manager

![Opero Hotel Johor Jobs Ads Oct 2020!](/assets/images/2020-10/opero-hotel-johor-vacancies-2020.jpg "Opero Hotel Johor Jobs 2020")

### How to Apply
Please email your comprehensive resume with current and expected salary to
**hr.opero@klana-msb.com.my** or **careers@operohotel.com**
Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.
